text: José Duarte (born July 6, 1980) is a Brazilian football striker who currently plays for Shenyang Shenbei in the China League One. He previously played for Maccabi Tel Aviv, Anapolina, Club Brugge, Hapoel Be'er Sheva, Hapoel Nazareth Illit, Hapoel Kfar Saba, Guangzhou Pharmaceutical and Chongqing Lifan.
